---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../components/Text.astro";
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
import CarouselImage from '../components/CarouselImage.astro';

---

<MainLayout title="winner">
  <!-- Fullscreen wallpaper section -->
<section class="relative bg-[url('/winner_img/bg-winner.webp')] bg-cover bg-top min-h-screen flex items-start mt-20">

  <div class="bg-black/50 w-full md:mx-40 sm:h-200 min-h-[600px] lg:h-300 flex lg:p-8">
  
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap- w-full">
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
        <div class="js-observe">
          <Heading htmlheading="h1" size="xl-large" font="lilita-one" stylingclasses="text-white leading-none pl-5 ">
            WINNERS <br> AND <br> NOMINEES <br> 2025
          </Heading>
        </div>

        <Text stylingclasses="text-white">
          We’re deeply grateful to everyone who joined us in celebrating Instant Day. 
          Your support, creativity, and enthusiasm made this event TRULY special.
          To our winners and nominees - you’ve inspired us with your talent and dedication.
          Thank you for being part of this journey and for making Instant Day unforgettable!
        </Text>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <Text stylingclasses="text-white pt-0 lg:text-right lg:mt-3 max-w-100">
          Instant Day was quite a success with more than 100 contributions. 
          So it was difficult to find a winner. After a couple of long but 
          exciting days, the judges agreed on the winner and the 10 nominees.
        </Text>
        <img src="/winner_img/crown.webp" alt="Crown" class="invisible absolute bottom-4 right-4 w-1/2 lg:w-3/3 lg:visible" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="lg:pt-30 pb-18 lg:flex flex-row justify-center">
  <div class="relative inline-block">
    <!-- Winner Image -->
    <img 
      src="/winner_img/winner-polaroid.webp" 
      alt="the winner" 
      class="mb-auto opacity-0 js-observe">

    <!-- Trophy Image Overlay -->
    <img 
      src="/winner_img/trophy.webp" 
      alt="trophy" 
      class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-45 h-45 lg:bottom-25 lg:left-75  animate-wiggle animate-infinite animate-duration-[2500ms] animate-ease-in-out">
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-150 js-observe">
    <div class="ml-10">
      <Heading htmlheading="h2" size="medium" font="lilita-one">
        WINNER - “The crowned”
      </Heading>
    </div>
    <div class="ml-5">
      <Text>
        This powerful shot captures more than just a man singing on stage—it embodies the raw
        emotion, energy, and joy that live music brings. The crown resting on his head symbolizes
        the triumph of the moment, celebrating not only his performance but also the spirit of
        confidence and passion that shines through. This image stood out for its perfect blend of
        artistry and storytelling, making it our well-deserved Polaroid Winner.
      </Text>
      <Text>
        The judges were especially impressed by how naturally the photograph conveys both strength
        and vulnerability. They praised the way the crown adds a playful yet symbolic touch,
        elevating the scene from a simple performance to a true statement of stage presence. It was
        this striking mix of authenticity and creativity that secured the win.
      </Text>
      <Text>
        “This photo makes you feel like you’re right there in the crowd, witnessing a star being crowned.” - Jury statement
      </Text>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <section class="w-screen overflow-hidden relative">
    <div class="rotate-5 origin-top-left -ml-12 -mr-12">
      <!-- Scrolling Heading -->
      <div class="overflow-hidden">
        <h1 class="animate-marquee whitespace-nowrap text-3xl font-bold font-lilita-one">
          NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES NOMINEES
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- First Carousel -->
      <div class="overflow-hidden mt-4">
        <div class="carousel flex overflow-x-auto space-x-4 px-6 scrollbar-hide">
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/beer-guy.webp" alt="beer guy" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/the-king.webp" alt="the king" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/the-dance.webp" alt="the dance" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/foodies.webp" alt="redbull" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/beer-guy.webp" alt="beer guy" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/the-king.webp" alt="the king" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/the-dance.webp" alt="the dance" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/foodies.webp" alt="redbull" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/beer-guy.webp" alt="beer guy" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/the-king.webp" alt="the king" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/the-dance.webp" alt="the dance" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/foodies.webp" alt="redbull" />

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Second Carousel -->
      <div class="overflow-hidden mt-4 pb-50">
        <div class="carousel flex overflow-x-auto space-x-4 px-6 scrollbar-hide">
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/alko.webp" alt="alko" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/redbull-crowd.webp" alt="redbull crowd" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/wonder.webp" alt="wonder" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/cityvibe.webp" alt="cityvibe" />
          <CarouselImage src="/winner_img/crowd.webp" alt="crowd" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.remove("opacity-0");
          entry.target.classList.add(
            "animate-fade",
            "animate-duration-[800ms]",
            "animate-ease-linear"
          );
          observer.unobserve(entry.target); // animate once
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.2 });

    document.querySelectorAll(".js-observe").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>

  <style>
    @keyframes marquee {
      0% { transform: translateX(0%); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    }

    .animate-marquee {
      display: inline-block;
      animation: marquee 55s linear infinite;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
